                        <summary/>
                        
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                            <locus from="1r" to="49v"/>
                            <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1495GadlaS">Gadla Sāmuʾel za-Dabra Hālleluyā</title>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                            <note>Excerpts copied from another manuscript, see <ref target="#e3"/>.</note>
                            <note>The death of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS8483Samuel">Sāmuʾel</persName> on the 26 Ḥamle in the 35th year of
                                the reign of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS8595SayfaAr">Sayfa ʾArʿad</persName>is described on <locus target="#31v"/>.</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                                <locus from="1r" to="2r"/>
                                ባርክ፡ እግዚኦ፡ በየማንከ፡ ዘንተ፡ ድርሳነ፡ ለነቢበ፡ ምሥጢራትከ፡ ዘኢያአምር፡ ትካት። ከዐው፡ ላዕሌየ፡ መንፈሰ፡ አሶት፡ መንፈሰ፡ አእምሮ፡ መንፈሰ፡ ጥበብ፡ ወልቡና፡ 
                                መንፈሰ፡ ረድኤት፡ ወኃይል።
                                <gap reason="ellipsis"/><pb n="1v"/><gap reason="ellipsis"/>
                                 በስመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ አብ፡ በአየረ፡ ሰማይ፡ ለግሜ፡ ዘያሕረገርጎ። ወበስመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ወልድ፡ በከርሠ፡ ደመና፡ ረቂቅ፡ ለማየ፡ ባሕር፡ ዘይመዝጎ። ወበስመ፡ 
                                 እግዚአብሔር፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ምስሌሆሙ፡ ዘይሤለስ፡ በተዘውጎ።
                                እሎንተ፡ ሠለስተ፡ አስማተ፡ ተአሚንየ፡ እዌጥን፡ ከመ<supplied reason="omitted">፡</supplied> እጽሐፍ፡ ወእንግር፡ ገድሎ፡ ለአብ፡ ክቡር፡ አባ፡ 
                                ሳሙኤል፡ ዘፈጸመ፡ ተቃሕዎቶሙ፡ ለቅዱሳን፡ ተሐራምያን፡ በውስተ፡ በዓተ፡ መዝግብት፡ እንተ፡ ይእቲ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ዘኢታሐፅፅ፡ እምደብረ፡ ሲና፡ ወደብረ፡ ዘይት፡ 
                                ወዓዲ፡ እምደብረ፡ ታቦር፡ ወደብረ፡ ጽዮን። እስመ፡ መራ<pb n="2r"/>ደ፡ ቃል፡ ይእቲ፡ ከማሆን። ዝኬ፡ ውእቱ፡ ዘይትነበብ፡ አመ፡
                                ፳፡ ወ፪፡ ለወርኃ፡ ሐምሌ፡ በሰላመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን።
                              </incipit>
                        </msItem>
                        
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                            <locus from="49v" to="50r"/>
                            <title type="incomplete">Three miracles of St George</title>
                            <note>Excerpts copied from another manuscript, see <ref target="#e3"/>.</note>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                            
                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.1">
                                <locus target="#49v"/>
                                <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6274MGFireHouse">Miracle of St George: The house of a monk is saved from
          fire</title>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                                    ተአምሪሁ፡ ለቅዱስ፡ ጊዮርጊስ። ወኮነ፡ በ፩ እመዋዕል፡ አውዓየ፡ እሳተ፡ ቤቶ፡ ለ፩፡ ብእሲ፡ ወበጎሩ፡
                                    ሀሎ፡ ፩፡ መነኮስ፡ ወተመይጠ፡ እሳት፡ መንገለ፡ ቤቱ፡ ለውእቱ፡ መነኮስ፡ ወለውለወ፡ ልሳኖ፡ ከመ፡ ያውዒ፡ ቤቶ። ወጸርሐ፡ እንዘ፡ ይብል፡ ኦቅዱስ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ ርድአኒ።
                                </incipit>
                            </msItem>
                            
                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.2">
                                <locus target="#49v"/>
                                <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6275MGHeathenArmy">Miracle of St George: A governor sees in a dream how he
          defeats an army of the heathens</title>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                                    ተአምሪሁ፡ ለቅዱስ፡ ጊዮርጊስ። ወበ፩፡ እመዋል፡ ወፅኡ፡ አረሚ፡ ብሔረ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ ከመ፡ ይፅብኡ።
                                    ወርእየ፡ ፩፡ መኰንን፡ በሕልሙ፡ ይቤ፡ ዓገቱኒ፡ ሠራዊት፡ ብዙኃን፡ ወ<add place="below">ኃ</add>ደጉኒ፡ እለ፡ ምስሌየ፡ ወጐዩ።
                                </incipit>
                            </msItem>
                            
                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.3">
                                <locus from="49v" to="50r"/>
                                <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7356MGHead"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: LIT7356MGHead</span></title>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                                    ተአምሪሁ፡ ለቅዱስ፡ ጊዮርጊስ። ወሀሎ፡ ፩፡ ወልድ፡ ዘደወየ፡ ርእሶ፡ በዓቢይ፡ ሕማመ፡ ዓበቅ፡ እስከ፡
                                    ፀጕረ፡ ቀራንብቲሁ፡ ኮነ፡ ዓበቀ። ወቦአ፡ ውስተ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያኑ፡ ለቅዱስ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ ወተቀብአ፡ እምቅብአ፡ ማኅቶት፡ ዘቤተ፡
                                    ክርስቲ<pb n="50r"/>ያን፡ ወተፈወሰ፡ ሶቤሃ።
                                </incipit>
                            </msItem>
                        </msItem>
                        
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                            <locus from="50r" to="64r"/>
                            <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7352HagDosGM"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: LIT7352HagDosGM</span></title>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i3.1">
                            <locus from="50r" to="62r"/>
                            <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1453GadlaG">Gadla Gabra Masqal za-Gutamālā</title>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                            <note>Excerpts copied from another manuscript, see <ref target="#e3"/>.</note>
                            <note>On <locus target="#59v"/>, a letter sent by <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS4333GabraMa">Gabra Masqal</persName> to
                                <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS3429DawitII">Dāwit II</persName> is mentioned.</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                                <locus target="#50r"/>
                                ንዌጥን፡ <choice><sic>ጺ</sic><corr>ጸ</corr></choice>ሒፈ፡ ዜና፡ ገድል፡ ዘአቡነ፡ ቅዱስ፡ አባ፡ ገብረ፡ መስቀል። 
                                ወኮነ፡ ስመ፡ አቡሁ፡ ተክለ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ወስመ፡ እሙ፡ ትርድአነ፡ ማርያም፡ ወሀገረ፡ ሙላዱሰ፡ ምድረ፡ ሰራዌ፡
                                ዘትሰመይ፡ ጕንደት፡ እስመ፡ እሉ፡ ቅዱሳን፡ አበወ፡ ዝንቱ፡ ቅዱስ፡
                            </incipit>
                        </msItem>
                        
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i3.2">
                            <locus from="62r" to="64r"/>
                            <title type="incomplete">Five miracles of Gabra Masqal za-Gutamālā</title>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                            <note>Excerpts copied from another manuscript, see <ref target="#e3"/>.</note>
                            
                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i3.2.1">
                                <locus target="#62r"/>
                                <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7347MGMTazkar"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: LIT7347MGMTazkar</span></title>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                                    ፩፡ ተአምሪሁ፡ ለአቡነ፡ ገብረ፡ መስቀል። ወእምዝ፡ በ፵፡ ዕለት፡ እምዘአዕረፈ፡ ተጋብኡ፡ ብዙኃን፡ ሰብእ፡ እምለፌ፡
                                    ወለፌ፡ ከመ፡ ይግበሩ፡ ተዝካሮ፡ ወይንሥኡ፡ በረከቶ፡ ወአኃውኒ፡ መነኮሳት፡ እንዘ፡ ያስትዳልው፡ ኅብስተ፡ ወጽዋዓ፡ ለተዝካር፡ ከመ፡ 
                                    የሀቡ፡ ለአናግድ። ሶቤሃ፡ ወረደ፡ በረከት፡ እምሰማይ፡ ላዕለ፡ ኅብስት፡
                                    ወጽዋዕ፡ እስከ፡ መልአ፡ ቤተ፡ ወተቀድሐ፡ እምነ፡ አሐዱ፡ ቀሱት፡
                                    ፵፡ ኮራ። ወእለ፡ ርእዩ፡ ዘንተ፡ አንከሩ፡ ጥቀ፡ ወአስተዓፀቡ፡ እምተአምሪሁ፡ ወዜነው፡ ለኵሉ፡ ሰብእ።
                                </incipit>
                            </msItem>
                            
                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i3.2.2">
                                <locus from="62r"/>
                                <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7348MGMWater"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: LIT7348MGMWater</span></title>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                                    ፪፡ ተአምሪሁ፡ ለአቡነ፡ ገብረ፡ መስቀል። ወካዕበ፡ በውእቱ፡ ዕለት፡ አርብዓሁ፡ ፈቀደ፡ አሐዱ፡
                                    ብእሲ፡ ከመ፡ ያእቱ፡ ማየ፡ ለተዝካሩ፡ ለአቡነ፡ ገብረ፡ መስቀል፡ ቀዲሆ፡ እምነ፡ ፈለግ። ወነሥአ፡
                                    ሐምሐመ፡ ወሖረ፡ ውስተ፡ ፈለግ፡ ወቀድሕ፡ ቦቱ፡ ማየ፡
                                </incipit>
                            </msItem>
                            
                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i3.2.3">
                                <locus from="62v"/>
                                <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7349MGMRobber"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: LIT7349MGMRobber</span></title>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                                    ፫፡ ተአምሪሁ፡ ለአቡነ፡ ገብረ፡ መስቀል። ሀሎ፡ ፩፡ መነኮስ፡ ዘስሙ፡ ገብረ፡ መስቀል፡ ዘመንኰሰ፡
                                    በደብረ፡ አቡነ፡ ገብረ፡ መስቀል፡ ወነበረ፡ በተጋድሎ፡ <sic>ብዘኅ</sic>። ወእምድኅረዝ፡
                                    አስሐቶ፡ ሰይጣን፡ ጸላ<choice><sic>ሌ</sic><corr>ኤ</corr></choice>፡
                                    ኵሉ፡ ሠናያት፡ ወኮነ፡ ዓማፄ፡ ወቀታሌ፡ ነፍስ፡ ወየሐይድ፡ ኵሎ፡ ዘረከበ፡ በውስተ፡ ፍኖት።
                               </incipit>
                            </msItem>
                            
                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i3.2.4">
                                <locus target="#63r"/>
                                <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7350MGMHealing"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: LIT7350MGMHealing</span></title>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                                    ፬፡ ተአምሪሁ፡ ለአቡነ፡ ገብረ፡ መስቀል። ወሀሎ፡ ፩፡ መነኮስ፡ ድውይ፡ ዘይነብር፡ በአንቀጸ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ እስመ፡ ኢይክል፡ ሐዊረ፡ ዘእንበለ፡ በበንስቲት። 
                                    ወኮነ፡ ይትአመን፡ በጸሎተ፡ አቡነ፡ ገብረ፡ መስቀል፡ ወዘልፈ፡ ያስተበቍዕ፡ ወይስእል፡ ኀቤሁ፡ ከመ፡ ይፈውሶ።
                                </incipit>
                            </msItem>
                            
                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i3.2.5">
                                <locus from="63r"/>
                                <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7351MGMTribute"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: LIT7351MGMTribute</span></title>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez">
